item.title: CVE-2019-10395|2024-08-04T22:17:20.568Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20build%20environment%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins Build Environment Plugin 1.6 and earlier did not escape variables shown on its views, resulting in a cross-site scripting vulnerability in Jenkins 2.145, 2.138.1, or older, exploitable by users able to change various job/build properties.
